Andhra Pradesh Corona Daily Report: 29 May

#AndhraPradesh reported 33 new local cases of Covid-19 & 52 cases from other states in the last 24 hours while 101 patients recovered in the same period. Total cases in AP stands at 3330 (incl. other cases)

 #Covid_19india https://t.co/IIwOPQXMwl
